('21', '60', 'Right after the customer left with the motorcycle, he came back saying that the engine light came on. I (Gustavo) told him that it was due to the service performed and that in 2 to 3 days the light would go out. If it didn\'t go out, I told him to go back to the workshop and we would diagnose it with our computer.', '2025-03-15 11:03:43', '2025-03-15 11:03:43'),
