('80', '67', 'During maintenance on the front braking system, specifically while cleaning the calliper, it was found that the calliper bolts were severely seized and could not be removed using standard tools.\r\n\r\nActions Taken:\r\nAdditional force and specific techniques were required to release the bolts, which demanded extra time and care to avoid damage to surrounding components. Once removed, the bolts were replaced with two new ones.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, upon inspection of the braking components, it was identified that the front brake pads were completely worn out and required immediate replacement to ensure the vehicle\'s safety.\r\n\r\nNotes:\r\nWe recommend regular maintenance and checks of the braking system, including the condition of pads and bolt fittings, to avoid excessive wear and more complex repairs in the future.', '2025-04-29 17:30:51', '2025-04-29 17:30:51'),
('81', '61', '15/03 - 11:45 start the job - The service will take 2 to 3 hours, the mechanics (neto and cleiton) said because it is a Piaggio Beverly and all the fairings have to be opened to install the alarm and tracker.', '2025-04-29 17:32:08', '2025-04-29 17:32:08'),
('82', '88', 'Firstly, we recharged the battery and carried out the necessary checks in an attempt to start the vehicle. Unfortunately, it was necessary to open the right-hand side of the bike for further inspection. Upon doing so, we discovered that the generator connector was heavily covered in dust.\r\n\r\nWe disconnected and thoroughly cleaned the connector, which allowed us to start the bike successfully. However, a loud and concerning noise was coming from the engine. Based on our assessment, this indicates internal damage which will require a full engine rebuild to resolve.', '2025-04-29 17:33:39', '2025-04-29 17:33:39'),
('83', '105', 'We\'ve checked your Spark plug, V-Belt & Clutch. Everything seems good for now. Rear tyre is not original on this bike.', '2025-04-29 17:34:13', '2025-04-29 17:34:13'),
