('87', '121', 'Just to Let you know we charge £55 Per Hour for Labour. It\'ll Probably take 2 hours to finish this job. \r\nPlease note, this list has been supplied by customer and does not represent work carried out or parts identified for replacement by Neguinho Motors Ltd.', '2025-05-07 15:37:15', '2025-05-07 15:37:15'),
('89', '124', 'We have inspected your vehicle and found that the connector between the generator and the ECU is burnt.\r\n\r\nTo resolve this issue, there are two options:\r\n\r\nReplace the entire wiring harness, as the connector is not available separately.\r\n\r\nRemove the damaged connector and make direct cable connections.\r\n\r\nFollowing our phone conversation, you have chosen to proceed with the second option removing the connector and establishing direct connections in the wiring. The cost for this work will be £80 labour .', '2025-05-28 11:14:39', '2025-05-28 11:14:39'),
('90', '127', 'Chain and Sprockets: Not in optimal condition Recommend monitoring closely and replacing soon to maintain safe and smooth Driving.\r\n\r\nTyres: Tread depth is low. Tyres are not in good condition, replacement is advised to ensure road safety and compliance.', '2025-06-09 12:48:05', '2025-06-09 12:48:05'),
